{"tid":654383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國歌法公聽會擾亂秩序　港獨男被逐離場","createTime":"2018-05-05T15:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T06:21:44.000Z","uid":28366,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0919b07772a42aeda39713d42f6792e9ab14e749","tid":654383,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/225910_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F225910_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6300ba09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/225832_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F225832_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b64f646c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">多名職員上前阻止，將陳家駒(箭嘴示)壓在牆上。</span><br />\n<br />\n立法會政制事務委員會今午(5日)繼續就《國歌法》本地立法舉辦公聽會，有出席的公眾人士在發言時大叫「香港獨立」被趕出會議室，香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒其後發言力撐該港獨人士，反批評立法會多名職員包圍該人的做法。 <br />\n<br />\n以公眾人士身份發言的學生獨立聯盟代表陳家駒，指香港年輕人近年成為奴隸，期間突然在座位上大叫「香港獨立、以死相博」，他更欲展示一幅藍色的旗幟，惟他未及展示，已有多名職員上前阻止，將他壓在牆上。委員會副主席周浩鼎指陳行為不檢，擾亂秩序，將他遂出會議室。 <br />\n<br />\n之後輪到黃之鋒發言，他指年輕人有撐港獨的自由，批評周浩鼎派7名保安將陳家駒押離會議室的做法。黃又說，倘若《國歌法》在本地立法，先例一開，恐日後《國家安全法》等全國性法律亦會在港實施，又憂中央以維護國家安全為名，干預香港施政，踐踏港人自由。黃又指港府高官的子女多在國際學校或國外讀書，質疑他們的子女唱外國國歌多於《義勇軍進行曲》。 <br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長聶德權表示，《國歌法》並非懲罰機制，非要強迫市民愛國，又指愛國情操不能強迫，期望市民勿流於偏激，應如立法會議員早前實地視察大灣區般，以開放及全面的心態實地了解。聶強調，觸犯《國歌法》的刑事門檻不低，須有足夠證據才能提出檢控，法庭亦會考慮多項因素才作出判決，重申《國歌法》的本地立法符合香港的普通法制度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180505/mobile/bkn-20180505162942816-0505_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180505%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180505162942816-0505_00822_001.html&d=1bCPV%2B0WBsW1rvVqQtkZ1Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=97f3f8e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180505/mobile/bkn-20180505162942816-0505_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"442c69c39536516663a98201667777a4b1c2cb96","tid":654383,"uid":12633,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:03:52.000Z","msg":"香港獨立！"},{"pid":"b529569b0e20b7407c448a7241a4080e7f5dfd84","tid":654383,"uid":28366,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"442c69c39536516663a98201667777a4b1c2cb96","tid":654383,"uid":12633,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:03:52.000Z","msg":"香港獨立！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/230703_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F230703_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=9447e2dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a14c2e0e54a5c04db5aea1740de74f875ae1abee","tid":654383,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:38:55.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"64d1c0ba0dfe595df501645e742535603aed3067","tid":654383,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T01:00:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9176ab11e5a7511d083478bacb7007aa80bb33d","tid":654383,"uid":9348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:53:41.000Z","msg":"有guts<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c69b970d3aba4a72afebf0b32fc8ce3a0d95e469","tid":654383,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64d1c0ba0dfe595df501645e742535603aed3067","tid":654383,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T01:00:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"家駒好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}